{"id": "1368076144611561512", "channel_id": "1368076144611561512", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "守密人的假期過得如何？趁著休假日，喚醒體們也相約外出遊樂：雲間迷藏、花卉攝影、逗樂貓咪、林間SPA……大家還挺會享受嘛！\n\n🌼歡迎守密人**在留言區分享你的度假打卡照**，可以是風景照、宅家照、帶喚醒體的出遊照…！\n▎我們將在留言區抽**3位守密人送上200銀芯的「假期基金」\n▎截止時間：5月6日 23:59**\n\n——◆——◆—— ◆◆◆ ——◆——◆——\n\nHow was Keeper's vacation? Taking advantage of the holiday, awakers also made plans to go out for fun: playing hide-and-seek in the clouds, flower photography, entertaining cats, forest SPA... everyone really knows how to enjoy themselves!\n\n🌼Keepers are welcome to **share your vacation check-in photos in the comment area**, which can be landscape photos, photos of staying at home, travel photos with awaker...!\n▎We will randomly select **3 keepers from the comment area to receive a 200-silver \"holiday fund\". **\n▎**Deadline: May 6, 23:59**", "timestamp": "2025-05-03T04:06:10.501000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-05-03T04:18:20.426000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "camera", "emoji_id": "1356053040251146460", "count": 12}], "attachments": [{"id": "1368076145333112893", "filename": "2.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 2303360, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1368076144611561512/1368076145333112893/2.jpg?ex=69cc99b2&is=69cb4832&hm=a037321ff6218236c65a76b1ef9f250fd73b936d25d58ecbaf517812b4128435&"}, {"id": "1368076145840357396", "filename": "3.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 514306, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1368076144611561512/1368076145840357396/3.jpg?ex=69cc99b2&is=69cb4832&hm=2e1ef364b3df52fd58d2cadf331ec612b9dbb2aeb8b1797439bf251fc9f135d5&"}, {"id": "1368076146503323658", "filename": "4.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 5594581, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1368076144611561512/1368076146503323658/4.jpg?ex=69cc99b2&is=69cb4832&hm=149a1efb696b18669c4896195097ea6782a50b3f4b4f6b38